song.info:
AMIGA 1200, DigiBooster 1.7 (8 channels).
The song comes from album "RetroBeat" DOWNLOAD: http://yerzmyey.i-demo.pl/
From the info tag: ******************************* This is my 6th song made on Amiga 1200 with standard CPU (Motorola 020, 14Mhz).
The song has 8 channels and has been composed on DigiBooster 1.7.
All samples by me (made on the Amiga, not on PC :) ).
Recorded from real hardware. (Stereo slightly modified).
Greetz to all AMIGA fans! *******************************
